<h2><span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<div class="references-small" style="margin-left:1.5em;">
<ul>
<li>Brow, James: <i>Vedda villages of Anuradhapura: The historical anthropology Of a community in Sri Lanka,</i> <a href="/wiki/University_of_Washington_Press" title="University of Washington Press">University Of Washington Press</a>, Seattle, 1978.</li>
<li>Codrington, H. W.: <i>A Short History of Ceylon</i>, <a href="/wiki/New_Delhi" title="New Delhi">New Delhi</a> 1994 (Reprint. Asian Educational Services)</li>
