e:Flag_of_Pakistan.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Pakistan.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/32/Flag_of_Pakistan.svg/22px-Flag_of_Pakistan.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Pakistan" title="Pakistan">Pakistan</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Somalia.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Somalia.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a0/Flag_of_Somalia.svg/22px-Flag_of_Somalia.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Somalia" title="Somalia">Somalia</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Yemen.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Yemen.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/89/Flag_of_Yemen.svg/22px-Flag_of_Yemen.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Yemen" title="Yemen">Yemen</a></p>
