t:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Saint_Helena" title="Saint Helena">St. Helena</a> <small>(including <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Ascension_Island" title="Ascension Island">Ascension Island</a></span> and <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Tristan_da_Cunha" title="Tristan da Cunha">Tristan da Cunha</a></span>)</small><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/South_Georgia_and_the_South_Sandwich_Islands" title="South Georgia and the South Sandwich Islands">South Georgia and the South Sandwich Islands</a></span><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Turks_and_Caicos_Islands" title="Turks and Caicos Islands">Turks and Caicos Islands</a></span></p>
