ki/India" title="India">India</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Maldives.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Maldives.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0f/Flag_of_Maldives.svg/22px-Flag_of_Maldives.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Maldives" title="Maldives">Maldives</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Mauritius.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Mauritius.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Flag_of_Mauritius.svg/22px-Flag_of_Mauritius.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Mauritius" title="Mauritius">Mauritius</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><span class="flagicon" style="margin:0px 4px 0px 5px"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Nepal.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Nepal.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9b/Flag_of_Nepal.svg/15px-Flag_of_Nepal.svg.png" width="15" height="18" border="0" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Nepal" title="Nepal">Nepal</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Pakistan.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Pakistan.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/32/Flag_of_Pakistan.svg/22px-Flag_of_Pakistan.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Pakistan" title="Pakistan">Pakistan</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Singapore.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Singapore.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/48/Flag_of_Singapore.svg/22px-Flag_of_Singapore.svg.png" width="22" he